      "path": "audio/narrations/gosper-curve/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.62,
      "size": 25920,
      "text": "有没有一条曲线，能不重叠地填满整片平面？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gosper-curve",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gosper-curve/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36576,
      "text": "戈斯珀曲线就是这样一条神奇的曲线，弯弯绕绕铺满每个角落。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gosper-curve",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gosper-curve/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "它的邻域是一块块六边形，像流水一样自然衔接。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gosper-curve",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "rule-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gosper-curve/xiaoxiao/rule-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.26,
      "size": 20160,
      "text": "我们从一个字母 A 出发，这叫公理。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gosper-curve",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "rule-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gosper-curve/xiaoxiao/rule-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.72,
      "size": 43488,
      "text": "每次把 A 换成 A-B--B+A++AA+B，把 B 换成一串对应的指令。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gosper-curve",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "rule-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gosper-curve/xiaoxiao/rule-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "这种字符串重写的生成方式，就是所谓的 L 系统。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gosper-curve",
      "section_id": "turn",
      "line_id": "turn-1",
      "filename": "turn-turn-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gosper-curve/xiaoxiao/turn-turn-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "把字符串当作画笔指令：字母表示向前一步。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gosper-curve",
      "section_id": "turn",
      "line_id": "turn-2",
      "filename": "turn-turn-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gosper-curve/xiaoxiao/turn-turn-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36576,
      "text": "加号左转六十度，减号右转六十度，正是六边形的内角关系。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gosper-curve",
      "section_id": "turn",
      "line_id": "turn-3",
      "filename": "turn-turn-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gosper-curve/xiaoxiao/turn-turn-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "一笔一画走下来，曲线就自动拐出六边形的轮廓。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gosper-curve",
      "section_id": "tiling",
      "line_id": "tile-1",
      "filename": "tiling-tile-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gosper-curve/xiaoxiao/tiling-tile-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.7,
      "size": 27216,
      "text": "每迭代一次，前进步数就变成原来的七倍。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gosper-curve",
      "section_id": "tiling",
      "line_id": "tile-2",
      "filename": "tiling-tile-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gosper-curve/xiaoxiao/tiling-tile-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "放大局部，你会看到和整体一模一样的形状，这就是自相似。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gosper-curve",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gosper-curve/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.28,
      "size": 36432,
      "text": "调整迭代阶数，看曲线从粗糙的折线长成致密的填充图案。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gosper-curve",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gosper-curve/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.06,
      "size": 32976,
      "text": "阶数越高，六边形的流水感越强，越贴近铺满平面。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gosper-curve",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gosper-curve/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "戈斯珀曲线用 L 系统重写规则，加上六十度转向生成。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gosper-curve",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
